Dependencies
libewf requires:
* zlib
* bzip2
  (optional for EWF2 support)
* libcrypto (OpenSSL) or Windows Crypto API (from the Windows Platform SDK)
  (optional but recommended)

ewftools require:
* libcrypto (OpenSSL) or Windows Crypto API (from the Windows Platform SDK)
  (optional but recommended)
* libuuid or Windows RPC API
  (optional but recommended)

ewfmount requires:
* libfuse
  (optional but recommended)


Also see:
* http://code.google.com/p/libewf/wiki/Building
* README.macosx

